title: Restores are painful to new iPhone
text: Restores are painful to new iPhone, not easy

title: Great when it works but it frequently doesn't
text:
I've got a couple of different O365 accounts that require use of Authenticator regularly. Frequent (1 in 5 attempts) will fail with various error messages even if I enter the correct number. Over and over again. Kill the app. Restart it. Lather.Rinse.Repeat. 
So frustrating.

title: Ông ơi
text:
Tóc Ông mầu trắng như gì vậy?
Tuyết có trắng không?

title: Best Authenticator app
text: It just works. Love the ability to backup your codes and the clean design. The peace of mind of not losing your codes has made me recommend this app over others.

title: Support for dark theme is missing
text: Hoping to see dark theme support added soon

title: Loss of watchOS was inconvenient
text: Need a way to bring back WatchOS authentication.   Yes, there is no facial recognition on a watch, but passcodes and response codes are sufficient without having to track down a phone for every MS login, email & calendar validation throughout the day.   Was much better with activation/authentication on your wrist.
